name: Block
description: Blockstreet is a multichain launch and growth ecosystem focused on accelerating USD1 stablecoin adoption. Through its dedicated Launchpad, it offers smart contract deployment, cross-chain launch support, USD1 liquidity infrastructure, and ecosystem integration. Backed by strategic partners and LayerZero tech, it provides development resources, grants, and advisory to power DeFi, payments, gaming, and real-world asset use cases.
